team_brainstorm_session_team2.text: let's plan our summer trip across europe
we could start in germany and try driving on the autobahn
yes! i’ve always wanted to rent a porsche and go full speed
then maybe head south to italy for some good food and wine
and wrap it up by partying in ibiza for a few days
sounds perfect, but we should also visit paris on the way back
good idea—let’s make a route map to see how much driving it’ll take
we can book a eurorail pass too, just in case we don’t want to drive everywhere
i’ll look up the festivals happening in june across europe
make sure we align ibiza dates with the big weekend parties
and maybe end the trip relaxing in the swiss alps
